   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"03s.html\">一覧　（サ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%259D%2591%2520%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%259B%2584\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　高知県出身。海兵卒。中尉でイギリスに留学。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　常備艦隊参謀として日清戦争に従軍。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　イタリア公使館付武官、常備艦隊参謀長、戦艦「初瀬」艦長などを歴任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　連合艦隊参謀長として日露戦争を迎え、<a href=\"../p/theihaci.html\">東郷司令長官</a>を補佐。旅順口閉塞作戦などを推進。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1905/05nihon.html\">日本海海戦</a>を前に、参謀長職を<a href=\"../p/ktomosab.html\">加藤友三郎</a>に譲り、第２艦隊司令長官に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、海大校長、軍令部総長などを歴任。死後元帥。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
